{"tid":1090144,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"「實戰」自資左$1000 出黎研究賭波","createTime":"2019-04-03T09:14:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T08:24:46.000Z","uid":123335,"like":47,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"ecdd11c823ba7975360fb0e536e5f725c2968322","tid":1090144,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:14:26.000Z","msg":"為左研究賭博既奧祕<br />\n我自資$1000 出黎作為研究經費<br />\n鑽研不同既賭波法<br />\n<br />\n今次既研究對象係6點日乙果十場波<br />\n我將會以四種不同角度既賭波法，去作為投注策略，測試邊一種方法能獲利最大。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>策略一：馬會反水流</ins><br />\n- 先查閱馬會分析，然後買晒對家 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gaHXu91.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgaHXu91.jpg&h=404c0433&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fFmYeBH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfFmYeBH.jpg&h=b4158d9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>策略二：共識流</ins><br />\n- 買入馬會分析及球探分析持一致看法既球賽<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZzuOBSx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZzuOBSx.jpg&h=775584ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>策略三：黃金比例流</ins><br />\n- 黃金比例（1.618 ~ 1.62）帶有神秘力量，適用於工業、建築及藝術設計等不同範疇，其潛力無法估計<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJbJqK3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJbJqK3.jpg&h=d5976b0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>策略四：落飛流</ins><br />\n- 買入尾盤時段落飛既球隊 <br />\n（後補，將於545pm時買入）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家估下邊一種策略最可行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d612339e02f7ff82a05ce2d818e476c50ee9e1d4","tid":1090144,"uid":34962,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:15:36.000Z","msg":"策略5 買你對家流<br />\n<br />\n你買乜買你相反"},{"pid":"da37db765f6d3e865e2f7b34961c9845a0f9f55e","tid":1090144,"uid":99700,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:16:22.000Z","msg":"彪哥流<br />\n先參考彪析<br />\n然後買哂對家"},{"pid":"badd6c88a01056e38fb844c7a4c4680d61ab5cdd","tid":1090144,"uid":73241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:16:55.000Z","msg":"lm睇上升下降軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nbetween有冇興奮感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e274871ce2e697b0e92cc61d736ba428a0898b31","tid":1090144,"uid":799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:18:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c852ccb901f636bc2b600c2492f23fa69ee30f0a","tid":1090144,"uid":206337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:21:23.000Z","msg":"勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />馬會因爲你要執笠了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70405ba8d18acb0225ee460b98568a6f84ba16c","tid":1090144,"uid":53430,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:24:32.000Z","msg":"太易得到既野 完全冇興奮感覺"},{"pid":"c39b5c2a66cb7499a2b9b14d0e221d4c463e629e","tid":1090144,"uid":47135,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:24:40.000Z","msg":"有無快感？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48bb1115ae7613902cafbedab7ddcd5a3391aa40","tid":1090144,"uid":28393,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:27:17.000Z","msg":"留名 中啲唔中啲"},{"pid":"59ad7995b25f2e1a58c07b6270ed46ae56c192d8","tid":1090144,"uid":63936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:31:12.000Z","msg":"黃金比例流可以試下跟外圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n馬會抽水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3640a703aa1c51bf3cd688b56c34e887074e8d8","tid":1090144,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-03T09:33:35.000Z","m